list.name: Deploys
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
   $__time(time_sec),
   description as [text],
   tags
  FROM [event]
  WHERE $__unixEpochFilter(time_sec) AND tags='deploy'
  ORDER BY 1 ASC

list.name: Tickets
list.rawQuery:
SELECT
   $__time(time_sec),
   description as [text],
   tags
  FROM [event]
  WHERE $__unixEpochFilter(time_sec) AND tags='ticket'
  ORDER BY 1 ASC

list.name: Metric Values timeEpoch macro
list.rawQuery:
SELECT 
  $__timeEpoch(time), 
  measurement as text, 
  '' as tags
FROM
  metric_values 
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY 1

list.name: Metric Values native time
list.rawQuery:
SELECT 
  time, 
  measurement as text, 
  '' as tags
FROM
  metric_values 
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY 1

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(time, '$summarize'), 
  measurement as metric, 
  avg(valueOne) as valueOne,
  avg(valueTwo) as valueTwo
FROM
  metric_values 
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND
  ($metric = 'ALL' OR measurement = $metric)
GROUP BY 
  $__timeGroup(time, '$summarize'), 
  measurement 
ORDER BY 1

panels.title: Multiple series with metric column using timeGroup macro ($summarize)

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  $__timeGroupAlias(time, '$summarize'), 
  avg(valueOne) as valueOne, 
  avg(valueTwo) as valueTwo 
FROM
  metric_values 
WHERE 
  $__timeFilter(time) AND 
  ($metric = 'ALL' OR measurement = $metric)
GROUP BY 
  $__timeGroup(time, '$summarize')
ORDER BY 1

SELECT 
  time,
  avg(valueOne) OVER (ORDER BY time ROWS BETWEEN 6 PRECEDING AND 6 FOLLOWING) as MovingAverageValueOne,
  avg(valueTwo) OVER (ORDER BY time ROWS BETWEEN 6 PRECEDING AND 6 FOLLOWING) as MovingAverageValueTwo
FROM
  metric_values 
WHERE 
  $__timeFilter(time) AND 
  ($metric = 'ALL' OR measurement = $metric)
ORDER BY 1
